{"comments":"Physical length units - real-world measurements.\n\nLeader module that re-exports all physical unit sub-modules.\n\n## Scale Coverage\nFrom Planck length (10^-35 m) to Quettameters (10^30 m).\nComplete coverage for any display context.\n\n## Sub-modules\n- SI: Meter and all SI prefixes (yocto to quetta)\n- Imperial: Inch, foot, mile, nautical mile, etc.\n- Typographic: Point, pica, didot, cicero\n- Atomic: Angstrom, Bohr radius, Planck length\n- Astronomical: Light year, parsec, AU\n\n## Design\nAll units convert through Meter as canonical representation.\nEach unit is a distinct newtype preventing unit confusion bugs.\n","declarations":[{"children":[{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"typeClassMember","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":"a","tag":"TypeVar"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Dimension","Physical","SI"],"Meter"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[287,28],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Dimension/Physical.purs","start":[287,3]},"title":"toMeters"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"typeClassMember","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Dimension","Physical","SI"],"Meter"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":"a","tag":"TypeVar"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[288,30],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Dimension/Physical.purs","start":[288,3]},"title":"fromMeters"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Dimension","Physical"],"PhysicalLength"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Dim